===Statements regarding Barack Obama and backlash===

Bush]]'s performance in office was a reason for the election of his successor [[Barack Obama]], and further that Obama would probably be known as the worst president in U.S. history.<ref>[http://www.cfnews13.com/article/news/2011/april/233988/Donald-Trump:-Obama-will-go-down-as-worst-president-in-U.S.-history Donald Trump: Obama will go down as worst president in U.S. history].''Bright House Networks''. Retrieved April 17, 2011.</ref>
